Class PatchUtilityTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • CCDD.PatchUtilityTest

  • public class PatchUtilityTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    aes A set of unit tests to exercise the new command line -patch command and associated patch logic. As a set of unit tests, these are sub-par due to the GUI dependency. These tests can probably be setup better with a potential to use shortcuts to drive the UI as necessary but for now they exercise some of the new logic.
